Module com.example.project3

Package com.example.project3

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Account
    This is the Account class responsible for all the different types of accounts including regular checking, savings, college checking, and money market.
    AccountDatabase
    This is an array based container database for accounts with all the different types of accounts.
    BankTeller
    This class is the main interface in which the user can input their account information for any processing including openings and closing an account, depositing and withdrawing money, and different ways of printing the information.
    BankTellerController  
    BankTellerMain  
    Checking
    This is the Checking class responsible for all regular checkings accounts.
    CollegeChecking
    This is the CollegeChecking class responsible for all college checkings accounts.
    Date
    The Date class takes in a String in the format "mm/dd/yyyy" and creates a Date * object with attributes month, day, and year, or can do so by default is we are * using the current calendar date.
    MoneyMarket
    This is the MoneyMarket class responsible for all MoneyMarket accounts.
    Profile
    The Profile class creates an object Profile using a String for first name, last name, and a Date object for the date of birth.
    Savings
    Savings class extends Account class and creates a savings account with the given interest rate and fees.
